Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.16,0:02:36.92,DefaultItalics,Man N,0,0,0,,{The gravitational field causes time to slow \Nso much that it nearly stops...}Lực hấp dấn lớn khiến thời gian trôi chậm lại...
