Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.22,0:02:40.55,Default,Michiyo,0,0,0,,{I thought I'd air out the futons \Nwhile the weather's nice.}Thời tiết đẹp nên mẹ mang nệm ra phơi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.55,0:02:42.92,Default,Michiyo,0,0,0,,{Don't lie around all day, all right?}Đừng cứ nằm ườn ra nữa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.92,0:02:44.72,Default,Michiyo,0,0,0,,{You'll be back at school soon.}Con sắp đi học lại rồi đó.
